<plot>Do you ever sit alone and watch strangers? That is precisely the hobby of James, a man in his mid-thirties. He spends his days observing people, taking in the beauties of life that most take for granted: the human smile, people enjoying nature, young couples in love. He ponders these events, treasures them until one night when he witnesses a man beating his wife. He must make a decision: to watch - or to act.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?641572</url></doc>
